oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.attachments.globalSearch.applicationModule
Class DeepEqualsStringArray

java.lang.Object
  oracle.apps.fnd.applcore.attachments.globalSearch.applicationModule.DeepEqualsStringArray

public class DeepEqualsStringArray
extends java.lang.Object

Simple class that replaces Array.equals(...) with Array.deepEquals(...) so that a Set implementation can be used to ensure only distinct items are in the list. It is only expected to be used by AttachmentsGlobalSearchAMImpl.

getDistinctPks

public static java.util.List<java.lang.String[]> getDistinctPks(AttachmentsVOImpl attachmentsVO)
Loops through the collection of attachments and returns a unique list of primary key values. The primary keys refer to the parent business entity for the attachment.

Parameters:
attachmentsVO - a collection of attachments yet to be iterated. The collection is only expected to be linked to a single business entity.
Returns:
unique list of primary keys. An empty list is returned if there are no primary keys.
